  P --> XOR
  XOR --> AND
  M --> AND
  AND --> POP --> ACC
  ACC -. next word w (×16) .-> XOR
  ACC == after 16 words ==> CMP
  CMP -. next class k (×8) .-> XOR
  CMP ==> OUT
